  <brief_title>WelChol® and Insulin in Treating Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Study of the Efficacy and Safety of WelChol® in Type 2 Diabetes With Inadequate Glycemic Control on Insulin Therapy Alone or Insulin Therapy Combination With Other Oral Anti-diabetic Agents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Daiichi Sankyo, Inc.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Daiichi Sankyo, Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to see how safe and effective and tolerable the use of WelChol®
      is for type 2 diabetes when added to insulin alone or in combination with other anti-diabetic
      drugs
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
